A Nigerian couple, Mr and Mrs Gafai, are celebrating their 50th wedding anniversary today June 25. Their granddaughter took to Twitter to celebrate them. She posted these photos of her grandparents and wrote ”Today we celebrate the golden jubilee of my maternal grandparents; 50 years of togetherness. READ ALSO Ikorodu Boiz to the world We are blessed to have you in our lives, the epitome of love, happiness and blessings. May Allah SWT continue to shower you with long life, health and prosperity today and always.”